<chapter id="Contact_Helpdesk"> 
<title>Contact Helpdesk</title>

  <section condition="TITLE=Cash Services: Contact Helpdesk; PERM=se_ctchp_access" id="CH" role="TOPIC">
    <title>Contact Helpdesk</title>

    <para role="TEXT">The <emphasis role="bold">Contact Helpdesk</emphasis>
    function allow the user to send an email to the bank helpdesk, for
    information or support.<indexterm>
        <primary>File</primary>

        <secondary>Contact Helpdesk</secondary>
      </indexterm><indexterm>
        <primary>Contact Helpdesk</primary>
      </indexterm></para>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Contact Helpdesk - Navigation</title>

      <para role="TEXT">To navigate to the <emphasis role="bold">Contact
      Helpdesk</emphasis> function, from the tool bar, select <emphasis>Cash
      Services</emphasis> &gt; <emphasis>File</emphasis>. Then select
      <emphasis>Contact Helpdesk</emphasis> from the left side navigation
      menu.<indexterm>
          <primary>Navigation</primary>

          <secondary>Contact Helpdesk</secondary>
        </indexterm><indexterm>
          <primary>Contact Helpdesk</primary>

          <secondary>Navigation</secondary>
        </indexterm></para>

      <para role="TEXT"><inlinegraphic align="center" contentwidth="100mm"
      fileref="../images/CUG_Cash_Services_file_helpdesk_nav.jpg"
      width="100mm"/></para>
    </section>

    <section condition="TITLE=Contact Helpdesk - Send Email; ACCESS=CH_01" id="CS_CH_Send" role="ITEM">
      <title>Contact Helpdesk - Send Email</title>

      <para role="TEXT">After selecting the Contact Helpdesk option from the
      <emphasis>Cash Services</emphasis> &gt; <emphasis>File</emphasis> page,
      a form will be displayed requesting the details of the email to be
      sent.<indexterm>
          <primary>Contact Helpdesk</primary>

          <secondary>Sending an Email</secondary>
        </indexterm><indexterm>
          <primary>Emailing the Helpdesk</primary>
        </indexterm></para>

      <para role="TEXT"><graphic fileref="../images/CUG_Cash_Services_file_helpdesk.jpg"
      width="160mm"/></para>

      <para role="TEXT">The form displayed by the <guimenuitem>Contact
      Helpdesk</guimenuitem> option for sending an Email, is as
      follows:</para>

      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>New Form - General Details</title>

        <informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="3">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="1.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="6.0*"/>

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Type</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel role="bold"> Entity</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_excla.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_EXCLA" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_action.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_ACTION" width="3mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top">Enter the Entity this message is being
                sent on behalf of. Click the magnifying glass icon to display
                and select from a list of valid Entities.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Topic</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_arrow.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_ARROW" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Select the topic from the dropdown
                menu.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <guilabel moreinfo="none">Free
                Format Message</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_excla.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_EXCLA" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_action.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_ACTION" width="3mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Enter the required message to be
                sent to the helpdesk. This can be a free form message, or a
                standard message (if applicaple) can be sent by selecting the
                file icon to the right on the message box.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>

        <para role="TEXT">After entering the message details, click the <emphasis
        role="bold">Submit</emphasis> button at the bottom of the screen to
        send the message to the helpdesk.</para>
      </section>
    </section>
  </section>

</chapter>
